===message:I completely agree with your post.  Lack of communication between Parliment and the colonies seems to be the primary cause of problems during this period.  I feel that the colonies may have been more accepting of Parliment's laws had they had a better understanding of what Parliment was trying to achieve.  On the other hand, since Parliment was clearly trying to benefit themselves with the implementation of the taxes and attempts to increase their personal revenue to pay their royals and officers, I do not see that even if they communicated their intentions to the colonists that the colonists would have appreciated their efforts.
=========yorg=========
